{"tid":1001031,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《黑豹》北美免費重映迎接黑人歷史月","createTime":"2019-01-30T00:16:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T20:14:09.000Z","uid":41343,"like":4,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1411bf3c919fdf471507263f199ccd97585114be","tid":1001031,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T00:16:21.000Z","msg":"首部以黑人為主的Marvel英雄片《黑豹》（Black Panther），不單票房理想，還是首部入圍奧斯卡最佳電影的Marvel英雄片。而為迎接黑人歷史月（Black History Month），《黑豹》會於下月1日至7日於北美其中250間AMC影院免費重映，迪士尼方面還會捐出150萬美元（1,170萬港元）到黑人學院聯合基金。<br />\n<br />\n另外，《黑豹》將會拍攝續集，之前有傳已死掉的奸角米高B.佐敦（Michael B. Jordan）都會回歸，演員昨日出席美國演員工會大獎時就更加肯定這個消息，他們說所有演員都參加《黑豹2》，演Wakanda皇后的Angela Bassett說：「所有人都會回歸《黑豹2》，我會假設，我們沒有見到Killmonger（米高B.佐敦）掉了落海，對嗎？」而「黑豹」查特域克保斯曼（Chadwick Boseman）就補充Wakanda會有先進技術治療Killmonger。"},{"pid":"8872ce5162b8acf01aa60c6b5cc5285747e4870e","tid":1001031,"uid":52590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又返生"},{"pid":"28444808b8c889ff41c91bf785674720993a924d","tid":1001031,"uid":197364,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8872ce5162b8acf01aa60c6b5cc5285747e4870e","tid":1001031,"uid":52590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又返生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:28:56.000Z","msg":"咁撚有型"},{"pid":"f0801638e42855d4de97cfc1b85a2bd7054c0c54","tid":1001031,"uid":197337,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:39:33.000Z","msg":"爆谷卡入奧斯卡,洗唔洗政治正確呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab013def4c26c7e6f828cb51cfaab015ac99263","tid":1001031,"uid":4596,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:42:55.000Z","msg":"On9 black history month 平時NHS d nigga nurse已經西好西面嚟緊一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15318c5f9d432